	<h1 class="title">东芝、松下等日本技术公司怎么都在忙着种蔬菜？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">丁叶蕾 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-11-19 08:28:59 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/3663/medium/3663.jpg?1436640931" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="3663" data-title="《东芝、松下等日本技术公司怎么都在忙着种蔬菜？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/3663/medium/3663.jpg?1436640931" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/3663.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
